    description: "Why renters insurance matters, what it covers, and how to find affordable coverage for your apartment or rental home.",
    href: "/guides/renters-insurance",
    category: "Insurance",
    image: "/guides-images/renters-insurance-guide.jpeg",
    author: "Screened Editorial Team",
    date: "Nov 26, 2025"
  },
  {
    title: "Building Credit From Scratch",
    description: "A beginner's guide to establishing credit history, from secured cards to becoming an authorized user.",
    href: "/guides/building-credit",
